title: Another Metroid 2 Remake v1.1 - Windows/Mac/Linux/Debian/Android
description:
Another Metroid 2 Remake v1.1 by DoctorM64
Release Date: August 9th, 2016

A complete remake of Metroid 2: Return of Samus for the Game Boy, upgraded to (at least) Super Metroid-level graphics and gameplay. 

All releases (Windows, Mac, Android, Linux, Debian Linux) have been included in this torrent. Feel free to download the appropriate file for your operating system, and PLEASE SEED, even if you grabbed just 1/5th of the torrent. 

System Requirements:

Pentium III 600Mhz, 256MB RAM
150MB Hard Drive Space
